00116 void CDeleteDataDlg::OnBnClickedOk()
00117 {
00118     UpdateData( TRUE );
00119 #if( FMI_SUPPORT_A604 )
00120     //check to see if they want to delete all data first
00121     //if so, we don't have to worry about deleting other stuff
00122     if( mDisableFmiChecked )
00123     {
00124         mCom.sendDataDeletionRequest( DISABLE_FMI );
00125     }
00126     else
00127 #endif
00128     {
00129         //not deleting all data
00130         //need to process all individual check boxes
00131         if( mDeleteMessagesChecked )
00132         {
00133             mCom.sendDataDeletionRequest( DELETE_ALL_MESSAGES );
00134         }
00135 
00136         if( mDeleteStopsChecked )
00137         {
00138             mCom.sendDataDeletionRequest( DELETE_ALL_STOPS );
00139         }
00140 
00141 #if( FMI_SUPPORT_A604 )
00142         if( mDeleteActiveRouteChecked )
00143         {
00144             mCom.sendDataDeletionRequest( DELETE_ACTIVE_ROUTE );
00145         }
00146 
00147         if( mDeleteCannedMessagesChecked )
00148         {
00149             mCom.sendDataDeletionRequest( DELETE_CANNED_MESSAGES );
00150         }
00151 
00152         if( mDeleteCannedResponsesChecked )
00153         {
00154             mCom.sendDataDeletionRequest( DELETE_CANNED_RESPONSES );
00155         }
00156 
00157         if( mDeleteGpiFileChecked )
00158         {
00159             mCom.sendDataDeletionRequest( DELETE_GPI_FILE );
00160         }
00161 
00162         if( mDeleteDriverInfoChecked )
00163         {
00164             mCom.sendDataDeletionRequest( DELETE_DRIVER_ID_AND_STATUS );
00165         }
00166 #endif
00167 #if( FMI_SUPPORT_A607 )
00168         if( mWaypointsChecked )
00169         {
00170             mCom.sendDataDeletionRequest( DELETE_WAYPOINTS );
00171         }
00172 #endif
